author: Elizabeth BeShears
title: Decriminalizing midwifery is the pro-life position all Alabama Republican legislators should support
text: This session let's finally do the right thing for Alabama families. There are 30 other states that have figured it out, we don't have to reinvent the wheel, but we do need to get it done.
